## Your Checklist Before Hitting Run

```
✅ 1. IAM role has S3 + Glue + CloudWatch permissions
✅ 2. Glue job params → add --datalake-formats = iceberg
✅ 3. Glue job bookmark → Disabled
✅ 4. S3 → confirm payerkey=233 folder exists with JSON files
✅ 5. S3 → create athena-results/ folder in nontrauma-analytics-prod
✅ 6. Athena → run CREATE DATABASE claims_db_dev
✅ 7. Athena → run all 3 CREATE TABLE statements
✅ 8. Athena → set query result location
✅ 9. Glue script → pasted and saved
✅ 10. Hit RUN!
```

Complete all 10 steps in order and the job will run successfully!
